CSR1000V (R1)
FortiGate V7.6.4 (F1)

Setting up R1
R1
  en
    confi t
      no ip domain lookup
      line vty 0 4
        login local
        transport input ssh telnet
        logging sync
        exec-timeout  0 0
        exit
      user admin privilege 15 secret pass
      enable secret pass
      hostname R1
      ip domain name r1.com
      crypto key generate rsa
        2048
      lldp run
      int g1
        ip add 100.0.0.10 255.255.255.0
        no shut
        exit

Setting up F1
  config sys int
    edit port1
      set mode static
      set ip 100.0.0.20 255.255.255.0
      set allowaccess ssh telnet http https ping
      set lldp-transmission enable
      set lldp-reception enable
      set device-identification enable
      end
  diagnose device user list

